---
const builtAt = new Date().toLocaleString('ko-KR', {
  dateStyle: 'full',
  timeStyle: 'medium',
  timeZone: 'Asia/Seoul',
});
---

<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>복지정보.com</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light dark;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        background: #f5f7fb;
        color: #1a1a1a;
      }
      main {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      h1 {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }
      p {
        margin: 0.4rem 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>복지정보.com</h1>
      <p>배포 테스트 OK</p>
      <p>빌드 시각: {builtAt}</p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
